Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located adjacent to the M27 and Port Solent Marina.  Portsmouth is a major commercial centre on the South Coast located 21 miles east of Southampton and 73 miles south west of London.  Port Solent is an established marina and commercial location located 4 miles north west of Portsmouth City Centre.  Located 1 mile from the M27 (Junction 12) connecting the area with key surrounding commercial towns as well as the national motorway network. 

The property is a detached HQ style office building set within well maintained landscaped grounds.  Providing accommodation over three floors, the building was refurbished in 2016 and offers well presented, mainly open plan Grade A space.

The tenure available is a sublease or an assignment to expire no later than 28th September 2026, with an opportunity to break on 28th September 2021.

Consideration may also be given to a sub letting of part, for a term to be agreed.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Grade A Headquarters Building To Let

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The M27 provides swift access to Southampton, approximately 10 miles to the west and Portsmouth, approximately 12 miles to the east. The M27 links to the M3 approximately 7 miles to the west and Southampton Airport and Southampton Parkway Railway Station are within 7 miles. A frequent train service is provided from Southampton Parkway to London Waterloo and has a journey time of approximately 70 minutes. Light and airy, all the offices offer impressive views over the entrance to the building and the surrounding landscaped gardens. Eagle Point provides modern, air-conditioned, open plan office accommodation. High quality fixtures and fittings are utilised throughout the building and enhance the sense of a modern, professional work environment.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Solent Business Park is situated adjacent to junction 9 of the M27, halfway between Southampton and Portsmouth. The M3 and A3 routes to London are quickly and easily accessible. As well as local rail services from Swanwick Station, London Waterloo is just over an hour from Southampton Airport Parkway Station, with direct services also running to Reading, Birmingham and many other destinations. Yarmouth House is a prestigious office building providing high quality open plan office accommodation. The building benefits from a ground floor reception area providing access to the office areas with a central core area with lift and stairwell and WCs on the landings. The office areas are mainly open plan with suspended ceilings, LED lighting, raised floors and comfort cooling. Externally there is a car park with 87 spaces plus a further area for another approximately 10 cars.

The estate benefits from a number of local amenities at Whiteley Shopping Centre and is home to a number of major occupiers including Zurich, Nats and HSBC. A well-presented ground floor suite in a prestigious modern office building on Solent Business Park. The suite provides a high specification of accommodation.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
3 Waterside Place is situated on the harbour front, affording excellent views toward the Solent. It is immediately adjacent to the A33, which is the main thoroughfare through the city, providing excellent road access.

3 Waterside Place is located adjacent to Town Quay. Town Quay, is a commercial waterfront scheme which incorporates offices and the passenger terminal for the Isle of Wight ferry. Nearby office occupiers include P&O Carnival (headquarters) and PWC. There is a Starbucks within Town Quay and further restaurants and convenience stores within a short walk. Within easy reach is WestQuay Shopping Centre and the new Harbour Hotel in Ocean Village. The 

M3 motorway connects Southampton to London, while the M27 provides connectivity to Portsmouth and Bournemouth. Southampton Central station is located 1 mile to the north and provides regular direct rail services to London Waterloo (1hr 20 mins). Waterside Place is also conveniently accessible by bus. Quayconnect is a shuttle bus service, which runs between the ferry terminals on Town Quay and Southampton Central Station via the WestQuay shopping centre. Southampton International Airport is located to the north of the city.

Nearby office occupiers include P&O Carnival (headquarters), PWC and Lloyds Bank. There is a Starbucks within Town Quay and further restaurants and convenience stores within a short walk. Within easy reach is WestQuay Shopping Centre and the new Harbour Hotel in Ocean Village. This refurbished office space is arranged over ground and first floors.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Working by the water connects us with nature, allowing unrestricted freedom of thought, enhanced wellbeing and increased productivity. The Boathouse at Town Quay boasts exceptional views of Southampton Water and Town Quay Marina, while providing a city centre business location with excellent road, rail and ferry links, creating a unique environment for your business employees and a perfect work-life balance. The Boathouse at Town Quay offers everything you could need for a growing business, with its own self-contained building, boasting spectacular views of Southampton Water and 1275 sq m (13,724 sq ft) of flexible space across 4 floors.

Southampton Central Station is approximately a 10 minute walk. The offices are on the ground and third floors of a landmark five storey building of brick facades. There is a manned ground floor reception with security, with lifts to the upper floors, and a lower ground floor car park.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Twenty3 is ideally situated within walking distance of a wide range of amenities that include shops, bars, restaurants, galleries, gyms, as well as all major transport links. It is also directly opposite East Park, one of Southampton’s most outstanding green spaces, and just a pleasant 13-minute walk away from Southampton Central Station. By car, Twenty3 connects directly to the A33, the main arterial route north from the city, where it connects directly to the M3 at junction 4. Heading south through the city the inner ring road links to the M27 providing easy access to the South East and South West respectively. Twenty3 Brunswick Place is being comprehensively reconfigured and refurbished throughout. Once completed, it will offer the highest quality sustainable design to BREEAM Excellent, the only available office building of its kind in Southampton. The state-of-the-art specification has substantial benefits for occupiers, keeping running costs low whilst helping them meet their corporate and social responsibility.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Totton is located approximately 5 miles from Southampton and provides good access to junction 2 of the M27. Linden House is located to the Totton bypass on Bartram Road. The property is located close to Rumbridge Street which provides a range of shops. Linden House is a detached office building constructed in 2000. The space is arranged over ground, first and second floors. The ingoing tenant may benefit from the current tenants fit out.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The campus sits to the East of the Brownhill Way roundabout less than 1 mile from J1 of the M271 motorway which provides excellent access to the Port of Southampton and wider road network. University Hospital Southampton (UHS) and its delivery partner Prime present this unique offering to join a new Southampton campus for health, innovation and commercial occupiers. The well-connected site provides a total of 9.1 acres across 6 plots which are suitable for various uses including offices, research and development, industrial and retail. Units will start at 3,700 ft2 and can be designed to meet occupiers’ specific requirements. Estimated completion Q2 2022

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located in a market leading position for connectivity, Aviation House is situated adjacent to Southampton International Airport and Southampton Airport Parkway mainline railway station, with excellent access to the M27 Junction 5 and M3 junction 14. Aviation House, Southampton International Business Park is a prestigious landmark office building providing high quality Grade A open plan office accommodation over 3 floors. The accommodation has been fully refurbished to a high-quality standard. The building benefits from a ground floor reception area providing access to the office areas with a central core area with lift and stairwell and WCs on each landing. The office areas benefit from recess lighting, access raised floors and data distribution and a floor to ceiling height of approx. 2.75m. Externally there is a private car park with 104 car spaces (1:179 sq ft). Which benefits from 16 car charging points and cycle stores.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Turnpike House is situated in a prominent position on the western side of Tollgate Business Park. Tollgate Business Park can be accessed from the north by junction 13 of the M3 (1 mile) and from the south by junction 5 of the M27 (2 miles). Tollgate Business Park is an established office location with numerous occupiers. Adjacent to Tollgate Business Park are many notable occupiers and local amenities. The property was constructed in 1998 and comprises a good quality, open plan office building. The available accommodation is on the 2nd floor which has been divided to provide 3 offices, a meeting room and with the remainder being in open plan.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Farnborough Aerospace Centre is one of the premier business parks in the South, comprising nine headquarter style office buildings. Chester House is situated on Aerospace Boulevard, bordering the western corner of Farnborough Aerospace Centre and directly south of Farnborough Airport. The town has excellent road communications with both junctions 4 and 4a of the M3 motorway only 4 miles to the north, providing direct access to the national motorway network via the M25 motorway. Farnborough is also well positioned for both Heathrow and Gatwick airports. Mainline rail communications from Farnborough are excellent with regular direct services to London Waterloo with a journey time of approximately 37 minutes.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
No. 8 Elmwood provides flexible, high quality space to suit your business needs. The offices, which have recently undergone refurbishment, are located on Chineham Park, Basingstoke’s premier business park and a vibrant business community. The space is available to occupy straight away.

Located just minutes from Basingstoke town centre, Chineham Park is easily accessible for commuters with a range of public transport options close by.

25 Templer Avenue is a landmark Norman Foster HQ building located on the main road of Farnborough Business Park, the impressive triple height atrium reception and break out space offers a welcoming area for visitors and staff. Set over four floors with views over the business park and the airport, 25 Templer has been designed to a high standard. The west wing of the third floor is currently undergoing refurbishment and will be available in Spring 2021. The building is well connected to the rest of the park and within a 5 minute walk to all the parks amenities, with a bus stop also directly outside the building.

250 Fowler is centrally located within the highly successful Farnborough Business Park, a mature scheme providing a unique base for national and
international companies. 2nd floor (9,416 sq ft) available from Q1 2021.

110 Pinehurst Square is undergoing an extensive refurbishment, presenting premium office space varying from 8,500 sq ft to 36,000 sq ft in a vibrant urban business park setting, close to the M3 motorway.

Farnborough Business Park is set in 125 acres, providing a diverse range of business space in an unrivalled location. Over 460,000 sq ft of offices have been constructed, with best in class office suites ranging in size from 500 sq ft in ‘The Hub’ to the 175,000 sq ft Fluor headquarter campus. An incredible and vibrant mix of onsite amenities include a 4 star hotel with restaurant, a day nursery, car dealerships, a gym with swimming pool, Costco, The Aviator Cafe, Starbucks and Costa.

Smarter Spaces are a selection of individual offices that are available immediately on either a short or long term agreement. 

Farnborough Business Park is one of the South East’s leading business parks. Set in 115 acres, it provides best in class office space along with a diverse amenity offering and events schedule that promotes the wellbeing of its community. The park is easily accessible by car as well as public transport, with a shuttle bus service connecting to Farnborough Main and North railway station.

Farnborough Business Park is located on the edge of the town centre, and is easily accessible by road, rail and air. 3 miles from J4 and 4A of the M3 motorway, 3 International airports within 1 hour drive time, 2 train stations in close proximity, served by a regular shuttle bus at peak times. The building is available by way of pre-let and has been designed to Grade A specification arranged over ground and 3 upper floors, with an impressive full height atrium reception.  The open plan floor plates will be regular in shape and designed to accommodate flexibility, with a single row of columns and the core located off the centre.
